                Popularly abbreviated as NEHU, the university stands tall in the northern part of Shillong in its green, lush picturesque and homely atmosphere. As one of the universities with potential for excellence, NEHU caters to students and scholars from almost all parts of the north-eastern region not to forget about students coming from other parts of the country and abroad. For more information, you can visit <a href="http://www.nehu.ac.in" target="_blank">www.nehu.ac.in</a>
